<plot>An Italian engineer, who works for an American firm, is asked by his boss to go to Italy and bring his niece back. He takes a lady friend on the trip, but is very surprised to find out that the "baby girl" is instead pretty much grown up and strong-willed. Worse on, she gets a crush on him, sparking a rivalry with his partner.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?200984</url></doc>
